    "Text" : {

    },
    "These requests call the same cloud intelligence client used by capture, daily questions, chapter suggestions, photo semantics, and notification intent generation." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这些请求会调用与记录、每日一问、章节建议、照片语义和通知意图生成相同的云端智能客户端。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This lab uses fixture-only data. It does not request permissions, save memories, or alter the production composer." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此实验室只使用样例数据，不会请求权限、保存记忆或修改正式记录页。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This mutates local debug data. Existing captureOrigin values will not be overwritten." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这会修改本地调试数据。已有 captureOrigin 值不会被覆盖。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This page calls the same repository and HomeBoardRuleEngine used by Today, then exposes the rule inputs, local preferences, and final visible cards." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此页面调用与今天页相同的仓库和 HomeBoardRuleEngine，并展示规则输入、本地偏好和最终可见卡片。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This page exposes the home memory desktop rule inputs, visible cards, user-controlled cards, suggestions, and preference actions before the formal UI polish pass." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "此页面在正式 UI 打磨前展示首页记忆桌面的规则输入、可见卡片、用户控制卡片、建议和偏好操作。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This page uses the same repository job stores and IntelligenceJobWorker used during launch recovery and background intelligence preparation." : {
